item.title: Dream Wolf Design - Orange/Green Colors Painting
item.description: The wolf native to the wilderness of Eurasia and North America. This design shows a dreamy painting of a wolf head in mainly orange and green tones. It makes for a great birthday present or Christmas gift for everyone who loves this awesome canine animal....
